  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-25">
      <h3>1. Sign Up or Login</h3>
      <p>Become a member and create your account to start.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-25">
      <h3>2. Unlock your Bike</h3>
      <p>Enter the bike ID code to unlock the bike at the proper station. </p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-25">
      <h3>3. Enjoy your Ride!</h3>
      <p>Ride your bike around as long as you want.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-25">
      <h3>4. Return your Bike!</h3>
      <p>Return your bike once you're finished with your ride and lock it at a nearby station.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

